{"id":"a_nv_0015","c":"nonverbal","s":"paper-fold","q":"Square paper ko do baar fold karke ek corner cut kiya. Unfold karne par kitne holes banenge?","figs":[{"shapes":[{"type":"square","fill":"hollow"}]}],"fo":[{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":1}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":2}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":4}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":3}]}],"a":2,"e":"Har fold number of holes ko double kar deta hai. Do folds = 2×2 = 4 holes."},
