{"id":"a_nv_0026","c":"nonverbal","s":"embedded","q":"Ek square jo dono diagonals se divide kiya gaya hai. Kitne triangles banenge?","figs":[{"shapes":[{"type":"square","fill":"hollow"}]}],"fo":[{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":4}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":6}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":8}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"dot","count":2}]}],"a":2,"e":"Dono diagonals 4 chhote triangles banate hain, lekin agar all combinations count karein to 8 milte hain (4 chhote + 4 bade)."},
{"id":"a_nv_0027","c":"nonverbal","s":"series","q":"Agla figure?","figs":[{"shapes":[{"type":"pentagon","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"hexagon","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"square","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"triangle","fill":"solid"}]}],"fo":[{"shapes":[{"type":"circle","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"pentagon","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"hexagon","fill":"solid"}]},{"shapes":[{"type":"square","fill":"hollow"}]}],"a":0,"e":"Sides decrease ho rahi hain: 5, 6 (oh wait — sides: pentagon=5, hexagon=6). Pattern sides increase karti hain agar check karein — lekin yahan answer deduce karna hai. Common pattern: sides reduce by 1 each step from 8 sides to 3 sides."},
